               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 22.</p>
               <p>RILEY - <rs id="t18270913-61-verdict369" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18270913-61-verdict369" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs> - <rs id="t18270913-61-punish370" type="punishmentDescription">
