               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 18.</p>
               <p>READ - <rs id="t18270913-61-verdict371" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18270913-61-verdict371" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs> - <rs id="t18270913-61-punish372" type="punishmentDescription">
